.UNINDENT
.SS \(dqis\(dq subcommand
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
path is [\-z | \-\-null\-in] [\-Z | \-\-null\-out] [\-q | \-\-quiet] \e
    [\-d] [\-f] [\-l] [\-r] [\-w] [\-x] \e
    [\-v | \-\-invert] [(\-t | \-\-type) TYPE] [(\-p | \-\-perm) PERMISSION] [PATH ...]
.EE
