.SS \(dqsub\(dq subcommand
.nf
\fBstring\fP \fBsub\fP [(\fB\-s\fP | \fB\-\-start\fP) \fISTART\fP] [(\fB\-e\fP | \fB\-\-end\fP) \fIEND\fP] [(\fB\-l\fP | \fB\-\-length\fP) \fILENGTH\fP]
