.sp
Groups:
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fB(...)\fP is a capturing group
.IP \(bu 2
\fB(?:...)\fP is a non\-capturing group
.IP \(bu 2
\fB\en\fP is a backreference (where n is the number of the group, starting with 1)
