(from 4.1.0) Fix error using \fBman\fP for the commands \fB!\fP \fB\&.\fP \fB:\fP \fB[\fP \fB{\fP (#11955 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:11955>).
