.SS fish 3.2.2 (released April 7, 2021)
.sp
This release of fish fixes a number of additional issues identified in the fish 3.2 series:
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
The command\-not\-found handler used suggestions from \fBpacman\fP on Arch Linux, but this caused major slowdowns on some systems and has been disabled (#7841 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:7841>).
