.IP \(bu 2
\fBmath\fP now also understands \fBx\fP for multiplication, provided it
is followed by whitespace (#5906 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:5906>).
.IP \(bu 2
