\fBjobs \-\-last\fP returns 0 to indicate success when a job is found
(#6104 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:6104>).
.IP \(bu 2
\fBcommandline \-p\fP and \fBcommandline \-j\fP now split on \fB&&\fP and
\fB||\fP in addition to \fB;\fP and \fB&\fP (#6214 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:6214>).
.IP \(bu 2
A bug where \fBstring split\fP would drop empty strings if the output
was only empty strings has been fixed (#5987 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:5987>).
.IP \(bu 2
\fBeval\fP no long creates a new local variable scope, but affects
variables in the scope it is called from (#4443 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:4443>). \fBsource\fP still
