.SS New or improved bindings
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
Pasting strips leading spaces to avoid pasted commands being omitted
from the history (#4327 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:4327>).
.IP \(bu 2
Shift\-Left and Shift\-Right now default to moving backwards and
forwards by one bigword (words separated by whitespace) (#1505 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:1505>).
.IP \(bu 2
The default escape delay (to differentiate between the escape key and
an alt\-combination) has been reduced to 30ms, down from 300ms for the
default mode and 100ms for Vi mode (#3904 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3904>).
.IP \(bu 2
The \fBforward\-bigword\fP binding now interacts correctly with
autosuggestions (#5336 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:5336>).
