\fBfish_ambiguous_width\fP (#5149 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:5149>) and \fBfish_emoji_width\fP (#2652 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:2652>)
