particularly the use of bright named color (#3176 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3176>, #3260 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3260>).
.IP \(bu 2
