#3211 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3211>).
.IP \(bu 2
\fBjobs\fP should only print its header line once (#3127 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3127>).
.IP \(bu 2
Wildcards in redirections are highlighted appropriately (#2789 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:2789>).
.IP \(bu 2
Suggestions will be offered more often, like after removing
characters (#3069 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3069>).
.IP \(bu 2
\fBhistory \-\-merge\fP now correctly interleaves items in chronological
order (#2312 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:2312>).
.IP \(bu 2
