\- in particular, \fB\-d\fP now means \fB\-\-debug\fP\&. The \fB\-\-dump\fP option
has been renamed to \fB\-\-dump\-parse\-tree\fP (#3191 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3191>).
.IP \(bu 2
