.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
Unmatched globs will now cause an error, except when used with
\fBfor\fP, \fBset\fP or \fBcount\fP (#2719 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:2719>)
